    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, add the cod fillets to a baking tray (use tin foil to avoid mess)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Drizzle</strong> with vegetable oil and season generously with salt and pepper</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
