      "instruction": "<p><strong>Spoon</strong> the tamarind glaze&nbsp;over the cod</p>\r\n<p><strong>Put</strong> them in&nbsp;the oven and cook for 8 min&nbsp;or until cooked through</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
